k\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pfj1665702684183.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pfj1665702684183.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pfj1665702684183.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pfj1665702684183\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__websetocc_249325\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sets the current occurrence according to the information received from the DSP\n      client.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__topic_d79667e1_d79668e1_d79669e1\">\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__p_d79670e1_d79671e1_d79672e1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__codeblock_rky_4mz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">websetocc</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__topic_d52417e1_d52418e1_d52419e1_d52420e1_d52421e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d249553e65\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7859e1_d7860e1_d7861e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7859e1_d7860e1_d7861e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7859e1_d7860e1_d7861e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7859e1_d7860e1_d7861e1__entry__1\"> 0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7859e1_d7860e1_d7861e1__entry__2\">Current occurrence has been successfully\n                        set.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7859e1_d7860e1_d7861e1__entry__1\">\n &lt;0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7859e1_d7860e1_d7861e1__entry__2\">An error occurred.\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> after\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websetocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_ERROR&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__3\"> An error occurred. Entity is the outer entity\n                        of a Record component.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__3\">The entity name requested by the DSP client is\n                        not painted on the component.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1133</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_OCC_NOT_FOUND&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pfj1665702684183__table_d7862e1_d7863e1_d7864e1__entry__3\">Occurrence could not be found.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__topic_d52422e1_d52423e1_d52424e1_d52425e1_d52426e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d249553e209\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__d6025e20\">Use in Dynamic Server Page components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__topic_d52427e1_d52428e1_d52429e1_d52430e1_d52431e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d249553e218\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__p_d79685e1_d79686e1_d79687e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websetocc</span> sets the current entity and occurrence so that triggers and operations execute in the correct context.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__p_d79688e1_d79689e1_d79690e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websetocc</span> statement is similar\n            to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span>. However, it sets the occurrence based on the entity name\n            and ID received from the Dynamic or Static Server Page client, instead of on hit list\n            position.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__p_d79691e1_d79692e1_d79693e1\">You can choose when to invoke <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websetocc</span>, but this should take place after <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webload</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reconnect</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__p_d79694e1_d79695e1_d79696e1\">Before using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websetocc</span>, a parameter list of entity names and occurrence ID’s must be set in the channel <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$webinfo</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(\"httprequestparams\")</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__p_d79697e1_d79698e1_d79699e1\">The format of this list should satisfy the following, where E0…En is a nested entity list in which E0 is the top outer entity, and E1 through En are sequentially nested inner entities.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__p_d79703e1_d79704e1_d79705e1\">Use the following ProcScript to set the current occurrence after reconnect:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"pfj1665702684183__codeblock_qzb_qmz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">reconnect/readcheck\nwebsetocc</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fyg1714374176100.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webload</a><p>Loads data from a JSON stream in $webinfo(\"data\") into a component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnx1665702574893.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>reconnect</a><p>Reconnect data loaded from a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct) with the occurrences in a component and database (if connected).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cib1665702561871.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Active Path for Runtime Processing</a><p>The active path determines where processing is applied in a runtime component, and the order in which it occurs. It leads from the current occurrence of the outermost entity down to the current occurrence of the innermost entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530896\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530896\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "websetocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sets the current occurrence according to the information received from the DSP client. websetocc Copy Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 Current occurrence has been successfully set. <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. Table 2. Values commonly returned by $procerror after websetocc Value Error constant Meaning -1 <UGENERR_ERROR> An error occurred. Entity is the outer entity of a Record component. -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name requested by the DSP client is not painted on the component. -1133 <UPROCERR_OCC_NOT_FOUND> Occurrence could not be found. Use Use in Dynamic Server Page components. Description websetocc sets the current entity and occurrence so that triggers and operations execute in the correct context. The websetocc statement is similar to setocc . However, it sets the occurrence based on the entity name and ID received from the Dynamic or Static Server Page client, instead of on hit list position. You can choose when to invoke websetocc , but this should take place after webload and reconnect . Before using websetocc , a parameter list of entity names and occurrence ID’s must be set in the channel $webinfo (\"httprequestparams\") . The format of this list should satisfy the following, where E0…En is a nested entity list in which E0 is the top outer entity, and E1 through En are sequentially nested inner entities. Use the following ProcScript to set the current occurrence after reconnect: reconnect/readcheck websetocc Copy Related Links webload Loads data from a JSON stream in $webinfo(\"data\") into a component. reconnect Reconnect data loaded from a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct) with the occurrences in a component and database (if connected). Active Path for Runtime Processing The active path determines where processing is applied in a runtime component, and the order in which it occurs. It leads from the current occurrence of the outermost entity down to the current occurrence of the innermost entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}